simple_test: test in a homogeneous bar.
inhomogeneous: test in a inhomogeneous bar.
ex_break_cfl: test breaking the cfl
ex_ok_cfl: same test as the previous one, but cfl OK.
undersampling: test undersampling the wavefield

In each directory, the script makemovie.csh can help to make movies of the snaphots.
You need GMT to be installed on your machine and run "csh makemovie.csh". The script just makes frame. You need to link them yourself
